  "detailed_description": "Step into the haunting realm of Bobo's Funzone, in this horror/puzzle adventure. Your mission: find your daughter, who was attending a birthday party here. Navigate the eerie corridors, unearth what happend, and be careful and cautious as Bobo is about.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Navigate Bobo's Funzone a kids entertainment centre as you look for your child</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/757a37a1d53305ecb0233a5b92f257f7.poster.avif?t=1761169299\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/757a37a1d53305ecb0233a5b92f257f7.webm?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/757a37a1d53305ecb0233a5b92f257f7.mp4?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Roam through the dimly lit corridors of Bobo's Funzone, a once joyful place now filled with shadows and ominous echoes. Your mission is clear: find your child amidst the unsettling atmosphere, where each corner may hold a terrifying surprise.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Puzzles With Found Objects</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/3648490ec36b906e3256d6557b6688b7.poster.avif?t=1761169299\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/3648490ec36b906e3256d6557b6688b7.webm?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/3648490ec36b906e3256d6557b6688b7.mp4?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Uncover hidden objects and tools scattered throughout the Funzone to aid your quest. Solve intricate puzzles that stand between you and the safety of your child.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the mystery of what happened here</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/0b20e041a36babb22e0cf849f836f311.poster.avif?t=1761169299\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/0b20e041a36babb22e0cf849f836f311.webm?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/0b20e041a36babb22e0cf849f836f311.mp4?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Delve into the disturbing history of Bobo's Funzone as you unearth clues that hint at the sinister events that unfolded within its walls. What dark secrets led this once joyful place to become a nightmare? The answers lie in the shadows, waiting to be uncovered.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be careful, you're not alone – Bobo is about</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/9510636a8f41f2f057a2f696dec771c7.poster.avif?t=1761169299\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/9510636a8f41f2f057a2f696dec771c7.webm?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703720/extras/9510636a8f41f2f057a2f696dec771c7.mp4?t=1761169299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Beware of Bobo, he lurks in the darkest corners of the entertainment center. As you navigate the haunted halls, keep a watchful eye, for Bobo is not just a figment of your imagination. Survival depends on your ability to outsmart and escape the clutches of him.<br><br>Will you be able to escape the funzone with your daughter?",
